lead_paragraph: Chris Young has homered with one out in the eighth inning for the first hit by the Boston Red Sox against Toronto Blue Jays pitcher Marco Estrada.

headline.print_headline: Estrada's No-Hit Bid Broken Up by Red Sox in 8th
